# GHSA-fjx5-qpf4-xjf2:
# RustSec marks borsh 0.10.4 as patched (`^0.10.4`), but Trivy's GHSA feed still reports it.
# Current 0.10.4 entries are transitive via Anchor/Solana lockfiles and are treated
# as scanner false positives until the advisory metadata is aligned upstream.
# Regression safety net: `npm run -s security:cargo:lock:check` fails if borsh < 0.10.4 appears.
